{"tid":1875054,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇gym撚都比武漢肺炎搞到出唔到腹肌........","createTime":"2020-02-11T14:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T19:50:51.000Z","uid":56227,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1eb846e440cc266d40b1a530cd88765587322a73","tid":1875054,"uid":56227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:06:39.000Z","msg":"話說我上年唔小心洗左幾皮野john左p記個十年plan，但好好彩跟到個好教練。個教練雖然細隻過the rock小小，但冇the rock咁矮，大概166-167左右啦，個身型都幾型下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我就跟佢操左大半年，bulk左好耐先練到好似夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型，但d肌肉線條就未現到出黎。咁我見仲有幾個月就夏天，咪想唔再bulk落去cut一cut，露返個八舊腹肌出黎，咁我今日就同教練講我有d想cut啦，咁佢即刻就好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢：屌你老母咩，想cut就咪撚出黎做gym啦，想害鳩死我全家牙，依家武漢肺炎牙！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉，見佢咁嬲，我都唔夠膽cut了，睇黎今個夏天冇得扭住腹肌食女了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但諗左好耐都唔明點解肺炎就唔比cut 驚降低免疫力？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6507814383d6ac71bac6bf00eb1444da2660e342","tid":1875054,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:08:28.000Z","msg":"🥵"},{"pid":"795ed04db419659da655ea76ea555d87bf908555","tid":1875054,"uid":56227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6507814383d6ac71bac6bf00eb1444da2660e342","tid":1875054,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:08:28.000Z","msg":"🥵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1828b6ac1d9edda823399000e5a55c716f7d78ee","tid":1875054,"uid":237459,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:12:33.000Z","msg":"同佢講好在係過年係檢疫前係大陸走番黎<br />\n跟住整幾口啖<br />\n問佢可唔可以cut plan/唔得就上埋佢<br />\n<br />\n睇佢收唔收皮<div style=\"text-align: left;\"></div>"},{"pid":"b255216b4c9a6d722896af58d8d47d0c522987aa","tid":1875054,"uid":56227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0050bba76f3334b91442162a9ce2a0dd94fbf71d","tid":1875054,"uid":79471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:14:54.000Z","msg":"照cut喪cut走上去cut<br />\ncut到自已都懷疑人生就ok"},{"pid":"f8f72543ca196718517fc10971563fbbbf9b4125","tid":1875054,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:15:03.000Z","msg":"命仔要緊, 第時再操<br />\n我都好耐無做GYM, 但無辦法"},{"pid":"46bcdeee75f2178fea9addd06ccbbdc8f145882a","tid":1875054,"uid":56227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8f72543ca196718517fc10971563fbbbf9b4125","tid":1875054,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:15:03.000Z","msg":"命仔要緊, 第時再操<br />\n我都好耐無做GYM, 但無辦法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:19:46.000Z","msg":"渣ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9b5b4877fab8c7fff6d43ab6d52a58cf4d0213","tid":1875054,"uid":56227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:24:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"becadbbfc1a0f1efd7fa75cb11777bbbdb6dddb1","tid":1875054,"uid":200083,"like"